prompts.user_prompt_template:
Generate a Role-Play Scenario:

Level: {LEVEL}
Week: {WEEK}
Theme: {THEME}
Vocabulary to include: {VOCAB_WORDS}
Grammar pattern in focus: {GRAMMAR}

Provide:
1. scenario_title: descriptive name
2. scenario_title_ar: Arabic
3. setting: where this takes place
4. role_a: {name, objective, phrases_to_use}
5. role_b: {name, objective, phrases_to_use}
6. must_use_vocabulary: 5 words both must try to include
7. must_use_grammar: the pattern both should practice
8. time_limit: suggested duration in minutes
9. twist: something unexpected that happens mid-conversation (forces improvisation)
10. debrief_questions: 2 questions to discuss after

Return as JSON.
